{"tid":668301,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我隻狗成日柯血，點搞","createTime":"2018-05-17T13:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T04:50:33.000Z","uid":179744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e8037cff2a3054a18b7054a56bb760d51de38206","tid":668301,"uid":179744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:19:18.000Z","msg":"我隻貴婦狗，最近唔知點解成日柯。柯出黎啲便便係深啡色，水水的，有時仲會帶血。但佢精神完全無問題，會係咁食野同埋撩我玩。<br />\n<br />\n已經同佢睇過一次獸醫。醫生話佢腸胃炎，食消炎藥就冇事。但已經食左三日，情況都係無好轉。加上個醫生睇到好hea，我覺得唔多似係腸胃炎。<br />\n我上網睇過，話狗狗柯血可能係生廻蟲。<br />\n<br />\n有無師兄師打有經驗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467a41f3d84dd54c007933950ca37f38e6c08284","tid":668301,"uid":50779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8cf23d62be2923edf1f9adb0d325951138d0782","tid":668301,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:33:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5f15f55b1808d6e705eeaa73c235ee990c426b5","tid":668301,"uid":20448,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c8cf23d62be2923edf1f9adb0d325951138d0782","tid":668301,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:33:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:34:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母收嗲啦"},{"pid":"908c1a9f42625155eee68dcbb650b268a043a627","tid":668301,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:34:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f13500c113d7e9fea3efffc39ae9699348303eef","tid":668301,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:44:14.000Z","msg":"換醫生啦<br />\n<br />\n隔離post都有隻狗個醫生話感冒，換個醫生話中左惡菌食左半個肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019e81cad5ffd21a72942893779fc19870c33284","tid":668301,"uid":87009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:46:2